c: 28
v: 48
t: "Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebefikelwa yiqiniso elivela kuthina bathi, “kungani enganikezwanga (izimpawu) ezifana nalezo ezanikezwa uMose na? Ngakube abakholelwa yini kulokho okwanikezwa uMose ngaphambilini” bathi “imilingo emibili omunye welekelela omunye futhi bathi ngempela asikholelwa kukona kokubili”"